name: Natalia Gomez
description: I’m a happy, healthy, adventurous woman with a real zest for life. I am a fiercely loyal friend and lover and expect the same in return. I’m known to have a quick wit and a sharp sense of humor…am a good joke-teller, but I have a funny take on life’s situations. You certainly don’t have to be a perfect special woman to earn a place alongside me BUT it would be appealing to me if you were confident, masculine and sexy!
